<h1>伊莉影片下載器～</h1><br />
<p>請將點開後有影片的網址複製至下方欄位，並命名主檔名。</p><br />

<%= form_for(@downloader, url: download_eyny_downloader_path) do |f| %>
  <%= f.label :url, "網址" %>
  <%= f.text_area :url, class: "form-control" %><br />

  <%= f.label :filename, "主檔名" %>
  <%= f.text_field :filename, class: "form-control" %><br />

  <%= f.submit "下載", class: "btn btn-success"%><br /><br />

  <p>下載成功後，請重新整理</p>

<% end %>

<%= link_to "回首頁", root_path, class: "btn btn-info" %>